title: Daz - Poser - SUPER UPDO HAIR (working hopefully)
description:
Hopefully this one works.  Sorry about the other one.


SUPER UPDO HAIR PACK

The Super Updo is the super package for your heads! Get your heads ready for the most classic and timeless styles of the Super Updo
package!

One package - 15 different looks


Mix one of the three base hairs with one of the five bun styles and create your favorite updo look. Whether you are going for a casual
side-parting look a strong combed-back style. This package has it all!

Have a look at the PopUp Promos below to see all included parts
and examples of how they can be used. Each style has been carefuly modelled and textured to bring you realistic renders! Choose out of 25 high-res and photorealistic haircolors
and even mix them with the included MIX matposes



Each part of this package includes fits for Victoria 4, Aiko 4, The Girl 4, Mavka and Genesis (Genesis fitmorphs fit the standard Genesis body / head. Scaled
bodymorphs are not supported)
